Netflix Content Analysis and Insights Report
Introduction :
In this project we use Netflix data to understand the Movies and TV shows content posting pattern on netflix.
Objectives:
Understand Content Distribution.
Identify popular genres.
Understand countries roles
Analyse ratings and duration
Study Content Growth over time

Dataset overview
Total records: 8807
Features: 12 columns
Key columns:
Type : Movies / Tv Shows
Country : Production Country
listed _in : Genre
rating  : Content Rating
date_added : Date Added to platform
Duration : content Duration
Data Preprocessing
Steps performed:
Handle Missing values (Replace null values with Unknown)
Convert date_add to datetime datatype
Created New Features
added_year
added_month
Extracted 
Duration number
Duration type
Remove Unnecessary Column (description)
Applied Feature engineering to explode country and listed_in.
Feature Engineering
Converted Multivalues Columns into useful format using .
	.split()
	.explode()
This helps in better Aggregation
Accurate Genre Analysis
Multi Countries Representation


EDA
